body: Youth to Youth Fund for Sierra Leone is now accepting applications from youth led organizations in Sierra Leone: "The Youth to Youth Fund is a competitive grant scheme for youth employment. It supports innovative, small scale youth employment projects submitted by youth led organizations from Sierra Leone."
